An '''outlaw''' is an individual that has defied the [[Laws and Customs|laws of the realm]] and the &quot;King's peace&quot; and are thus outside the protection of the law. A similar term, but with a more negative connotation, is '''brigand'''.

Outlaws tend to form bands or &quot;brotherhoods&quot; for protection and to avoid capture.
